@model EasyTalkWeb.Models.ViewModels.ProfileViewModel
@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Identity
<link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/register.css"/>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css//profile.css" />
<div class="container-register">
    <div class="page-items">
        <div class="profile-items">
            <div>
                <div class="profile-inner">
                    <div class="title">
                        <h1>Profile</h1>
                    </div>
                    <div class="input-form">
                        <div>
                            <label class="form-label">First Name</label>
                            <input type="text" placeholder="@Model.FirstName" class="form-control" asp-for="FirstName" readonly />
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label class="form-label">Last Name</label>
                            <input type="text" placeholder="@Model.LastName" class="form-control" asp-for="LastName" readonly />
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label class="form-label">Date of Birth</label>
                            <input type="date" placeholder=" @Model.DateOfBirth" class="form-control" asp-for="DateOfBirth" readonly />
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label class="form-label">Location</label>
                            <input type="text" placeholder="@Model.Location" class="form-control" asp-for="Location" readonly />
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label class="form-label">Email</label>
                            <input type="email" placeholder="@Model.Email" class="form-control" asp-for="Email" readonly />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                @if (User.IsInRole("Freelancer"))
                {
                    <div class="input-form">
                        <label class="form-label">Specialization</label>
                        <textarea style="height: 120px; resize: none" type="text" placeholder="@Model.Specialization" class="form-control" asp-for="Specialization" readonly></textarea>
                        <span class="text-danger" asp-validation-for="Specialization"></span>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label class="form-label">Technologies</label>
                        <div class="technologies">
                            @if (Model.Technologies != null)
                            {
                                @foreach (Technology technology in Model.Technologies)
                                {
                                    <div class="technology">@technology.Name</div>
                                }
                            }
                            else
                            {
                                <p>No technologies found</p>
                            }
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                }
                <div class="edit-button">
                    <a class="register-button" asp-controller="Profile" asp-action="Edit">Edit</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            
        </div>

    </div>
</div>